TOP(1)

NAME
    top - show process CPU and memory usage

SYNOPSIS
    top [-r refreshes] [-d delay_ticks]

DESCRIPTION
    top displays process CPU and memory usage. By default it refreshes
    repeatedly.

OPTIONS
    -r refreshes
        Stop after refreshes screen updates.

    -d delay_ticks
        Delay this many timer ticks between refreshes.

    -h
    --help
        Show usage.

EXAMPLES
    top
    top -r 1
    top -r 5 -d 20

SEE ALSO
    meminfo(1), uptime(1)
